title: Ganesha Goes to Lunch: Classics from Mystic India (ePub) 2007
description: Ganesha Goes to Lunch: Classics from Mystic India (Mandala Classics), 2007 This accessible collection of ancient India's most insightful myths celebrates well-known stories and others, not readily known to Western readers. These are stories of Vishnu, Brahma, Ganesha and the other India, as well as of humans struggling with some of life's essential truths. Paperback: 128 pages Publisher: Mandala Publishing Group (30 Sept. 2007) Language: English ISBN-10: 1601091028 https://www.amazon.co.uk/Ganesha-Goes-Lunch-Classics-Mandala/dp/1601091028
